101
00:07:04,990 --> 00:07:07,740
<font color="yellow">Dan tentunya, Ri Hwan juga
pasti akan mengetahuinya juga.</font>

102
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:08,840
<font color="yellow">Bibi.</font>

103
00:07:09,570 --> 00:07:11,610
<font color="yellow">- Bibi.
- Pulanglah.</font>

104
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,920
<font color="yellow">Tidak, aku akan tinggal
di sini malam ini.</font>

105
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,040
<font color="yellow">Pulanglah.</font>

106
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,220
<font color="yellow">Tapi...</font>

107
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:21,070
<font color="yellow">Apa kau mau membuatku
memarahimu lagi sekarang?</font>

108
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:11,280
<font color="yellow">Kim Haeng Ah!</font>

109
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:16,000
<font color="yellow">Kim Haeng Ah, Kim Haeng Ah.</font>

110
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,260
<font color="yellow">Kim Haeng Ah.</font>

111
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:21,870
<font color="yellow">Apa yang terjadi?</font>

112
