<font color="yellow">Kenapa ponsel Haeng Ah ada padamu?</font>

127
00:11:52,290 --> 00:11:53,740
<font color="yellow">Aku akan segera ke sana.</font>

128
00:12:09,610 --> 00:12:11,030
<font color="yellow">Apa sesuatu terjadi pada Haeng Ah?</font>

129
