130
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:13,960
<font color="yellow">Hubungi aku jika kau butuh sesuatu!</font>

131
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:27,450
<font color="yellow">Kenapa perasaanku jadi tidak enak?</font>

132
00:12:59,070 --> 00:13:00,730
