137
00:13:14,690 --> 00:13:16,940
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu jelaskan padaku?</font>

138
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,800
<font color="yellow">Seharusnya aku yang bertanya begitu.</font>

139
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,110
<font color="yellow">Kemarin dia tak pernah murung.</font>

140
